--- The irssi script ---

    0. Install one of:
       - Perl module Net::DBus
       - 'notify-send' from libnotify-bin
    1. mv notify-send.pl ~/.irssi/scripts/
    2. /script load notify-send

--- The server ---

The server is only needed if you run irssi on a different server than X11.

    0. Run: ./notify-receive.pl 'tcp!*!31337'
    1. Go back to your irssi
    2. /set notify_host tcp!1.2.3.4!31337
